Detailed Description

This is the App interface according to Bluetooth specification for the Basic Printing Profile. Descendants of this class have to override the OnRequestStateChange() method (BtService::OnRequestStateChange()). This method is called, whenever a request changes its state. If the request is finished, the result data can be retrieved using the according getter methods.
